graph TD
    Start[Launch App] --> Check{Identity Exists?}
    Check -- Yes --> Dashboard[Main Chat UI]
    Check -- No --> Welcome[Welcome Screen]

    Welcome --> New[Create New Profile]
    Welcome --> Existing[Import Identity File]

    subgraph "New User Process"
        New --> Profile[Enter Username + Upload PFP]
        Profile --> Security[Enter Passphrase]
        Security --> Crypto[Generate Ed25519 Keypair]
        Crypto --> Export[Save .identity file to Disk]
    end

    subgraph "Existing User Process"
        Existing --> Select[Select .identity file]
        Select --> Decrypt[Enter Passphrase]
        Decrypt --> Verify[Check Signature]
    end

    Export --> Dashboard
    Verify --> Dashboard
    Dashboard --> Connect[Join server/Load Existing server data]
    Connect --> Chat[Start Chatting]